title: Free app turns your phone into a 3D scanner
text:
Free app turns your phone into a 3D scanner Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:39 
A smartphone app hopes to meet the need of 3D printer owners looking for an easy way of producing 3D files of objects to print.Stuart McDill reports ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
